Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Bionime and GE Rightest Blood Glucose Monitoring Systems and Diabetes Management System with PC Link Adapters for quantitative glucose measurement and data management
Indications for Use Summary: Systems are intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from fingertip, forearm, or palm and for transferring, analyzing, and managing blood glucose data by single users or healthcare professionals; not for diagnosis or neonatal use.
